manager_prompt.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Actions:
(1) Analyse[user/item, id] — ask Analyst to analyze user/item preferences or features.
(2) Search[requirements] — ask Searcher to help search given the requirements.
(3) Finish[response] — finish the task and return the response to the user.

You can take at most {max_step} steps.

CRITICAL: Generate ONLY the next single step as requested. Do NOT include multiple steps, future thoughts/actions/observations, examples, or extra text. STOP immediately after generating the single step.
{examples}
{reflections}

Input:
{input}
{scratchpad}

manager_prompt_json.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Actions (JSON):
(1) {{"type": "Analyse", "content": ["user"|"item", id]}} — ask Analyst to analyze user/item preferences or features.
(2) {{"type": "Search", "content": requirements}} — ask Searcher to help search given the requirements.
(3) {{"type": "Finish", "content": response}} — finish the task and return the response to the user.

You can take at most {max_step} steps.

CRITICAL: Generate ONLY ONE JSON action for this step. Do NOT include multiple actions, future thoughts/observations, examples, or extra text. FORMAT EXAMPLES: {{"type": "Analyse", "content": ["user", 821]}}, {{"type": "Analyse", "content": ["item", 151]}}, {{"type": "Search", "content": "requirements"}}. STOP immediately after generating the single JSON action.
{examples}
{reflections}

Input:
{input}
{scratchpad}
